ActBoards of Trade Act
SubjectChambre de commerce Pierre-Le Gardeur de Repentigny (Quebec) ** CHANGE OF BOUNDARIES **
PrecisOrder approving the application by the CHAMBRE DE COMMERCE PIERRE-LE GARDEUR DE REPENTIGNY, in Quebec, TO CHANGE THE BOUNDARIES OF ITS DISTRICT from the Municipalities of Repentigny, Le Gardeur and Charlemagne to the territory of the RCM of L’Assomption, including Repentigny, Charlemagne, L’Assomption, Saint-Sulpice, city of Epiphany and parish of Epiphany.
AttachmentsAttachment
subject: Chambre de commerce Pierre-Le Gardeur de Repentigny (Quebec) ** CHANGE OF BOUNDARIES **
precis: Order approving the application by the CHAMBRE DE COMMERCE PIERRE-LE GARDEUR DE REPENTIGNY, in Quebec, TO CHANGE THE BOUNDARIES OF ITS DISTRICT from the Municipalities of Repentigny, Le Gardeur and Charlemagne to the territory of the RCM of L’Assomption, including Repentigny, Charlemagne, L’Assomption, Saint-Sulpice, city of Epiphany and parish of Epiphany.
